generateCinemaID(int) - Static method in class utils.IdUtils
integer to String conversion function Divides integer ID by 25 (we will save Z as a filler alphabet) The remainder will be the offset from A Assumption made for string ID's length = 3: total cinemas less than or equal to 15624 (25^3 - 1)
